name: A Warm Blue Thank You
description:
A special piece to Thank the wonderful Tezos Community for a warm welcome and continued support on my Tezos collections on HicetNunc, Objkt and Rarible. 

You have all made me feel so very loved and inspired to keep painting my heart out on my little iPad and to courageously immerse myself in the depths of emotions. 
-
So a Warm Blue Thank You to all of you and I hope this piece starts many thriving collections for first-time collectors! xoxo dreamingdigitally
